tool_description: Airbnb API allows users to search accommodations by location, place name, and GEO coordinates to find a place to rent. This API has all needed by any developer to create a new application with some extended features.
name: Airbnb_v2
title: Airbnb

api_list.name: Get Property Checkout Price
api_list.description: This API will return the checkout cost of the Property

required_parameters.name: propertyId
required_parameters.description: Required filed **propertyId** can be got from search property api as **id** parameter.

optional_parameters.name: adults
optional_parameters.description: Number of adult guests (13 years and over). Default is set to 1.

optional_parameters.name: pets
optional_parameters.description: Number of pets

optional_parameters.name: children
optional_parameters.description: Number of children (2-12 years)

optional_parameters.name: currency
optional_parameters.description: Default currency is **USD**. To get other available currency please call **Get Currency** API

optional_parameters.name: languageId
optional_parameters.description: Enter **LanguageId** if you want a response in the requested language. To get **LanguageId** call **getLanguages** API and pass in the Id.

optional_parameters.name: infants
optional_parameters.description: Number of infants (under 2 years)

api_list.name: Test API
api_list.description: This API is to test if server is up and running
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://airbnb19.p.rapidapi.com/api/v1/test"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "airbnb19.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
